snippet.title: Harpoon II gameplay (PC Game, 1994)
snippet.description:
Introduction and gameplay for Harpoon II, Dos PC game produced by Three-Sixty Pacific in 1994 - http://www.squakenet.com/download/harpoon-ii/7698/
Harpoon II is a simulation of modern-era naval combat. It has a variety of ships and submarines.
Played through Dosbox emulation platform.
Recorded with original sound.

Similar videos you may like:
Harpoon Classic - https://youtu.be/CwdXPMh7jnw
Harpoon - https://youtu.be/K1yo3ZBCQLc
Carriers at War II - https://youtu.be/chaV_Wznbag
